These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, dunhill, havana
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the dunhill-smoker and the havana-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar         | dunhill | oliveros   | havana |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, tea
City: paris, london, berlin
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person traveling to paris##7
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | tea | cola   | soy-milk   |
| City        | london | berlin | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, strawberry
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, oliveros, aristoff
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the dannemann-smoker##7
3. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the aristoff-smoker##8
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | nectarine | strawberry | cauliflower |
| Cigar   | dannemann       | aristoff     | oliveros         |

