.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, architect, bartender
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, country
1. the bartender is not to the right of the architect##8
2. the bartender is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the analyst##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | analyst | bartender | architect |
| Music-Genre   | country  | reggae | ambient    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
3 different games are played: go, snooker, mah-jongg
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
4. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person playing go##8
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg | go |
| Pet           | horse    | turtle      | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, security-guard
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, chess
1. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
2. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
4. the photographer is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | photographer | dancer | security-guard |
| Game   | chess        | scrabble   | poker     |

