.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, d&b, indie
1. the fan of d&b is between the fan of indie and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
3. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
4. the fan of indie is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | sprite |
| Music-Genre        | indie      | d&b    | trance |

