.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lilac, green
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance
1. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
2. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who likes red##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Color          | green | red  | lilac |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | drama | romance   |

