3. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | sprite        | juice    |
| Game      | monopoly  | poker | domino |

