2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Birthday   | october  | september | april     |
| Transport     | airplane | bus     | snowmobile |

