2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | mystery      | adventure |
| Sport         | badminton | basketball | tennis     |

