The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, boat
1. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person eating apricot##6
2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
4. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | orange | raspberry | apricot    |
| Transport    | quad-bike   | airplane      | boat |

