.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-19::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, turkish
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
2. the turkish is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the chinchilla##7
4. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the australian##8
5. the australian is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Pet   | ferret   | guinea-pig    | chinchilla  |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish | australian |

