.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, video-games
City: new-york, colone, hamburg
1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
2. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks | video-games |
| City   | hamburg  | colone    | new-york    |

 